Author: Fab√ò#8941
Content:
regarding the issue we have had with the founders CC causing a small inflation of supply,
we have reached out to JL777 who is fixing this issue as we speak. We have had multiple opinions on what to do with the funds, 
from keeping them in our reserve for future developments, to a complete coin burn of all additional coins.
There are currently ""31,742,881"" coins which have been minted from the founders CC out of a total circulating supply of around 130,000,000.

We would like to reach out to the community and find a solution that works with everyone, while furthering
the vision of √ò CryptoUnion. One of the ideas and feedback we have received is that we should make use of the
 funds in a fair way that  benefits everyone (Early investors, Komodo holders, OCU, New investors and Development)


We have taken into consideration the % of inflation, the current low price of OUR, the fundraiser investors, and the effects
that these extra tokens will have on the price action. We would like some more feedback on whether this would be an appropriate solution and would 
like to hear back from you, whether here or in private DM.

Author: Fab√ò#8941
Fab√ò#8941
Content:
With the very low liquidity, we dont think this additional supply would have much of an impact on price, taking into account our marketcap is below 1,000,000 atm and very low trading activity
it is more of an interest/publicity problem, and the airdrop will definitely help with that
I think that, along with burning any additional funds on top of whatever is currently in that address, would be a good solution


We think that auctioning off "additional" supply minted for BTC for purpose of furthering listings only and allowing more investors in really makes it work out to be a very good thing if it goes ahead
